{"ts":"2026-06-26T22:22:58.222Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"submit_and_exit","toolCallId":"8stuhbm6","input":{"summary":"Upgraded `/build/foundry-studio` into a premium visual workflow builder preview. \n\n### Steps taken and implementation:\n1. **Designed UI Strategy**: Built a high-tech command center workspace matching GFF's 2026 premium dark design theme (grid lines, subtle spotlights, glowing borders, custom SVGs, and monospaced typography).\n2. **Added Industry Presets & Topologies**: Integrated five representative, highly tailored industry presets (Banking, Healthcare, Energy, Telecom, and Retail & Supply Chain) with pre-configured domain stages and custom vector/ontology knowledge labels, as well as four cognitive agent patterns.\n3. **Created Live DAG Workspace Canvas**: Designed a responsive, interactive visual node system with premium node cards linked via high-fidelity, CSS-animated SVG path arrows.\n4. **Crafted Interactive Modifiers**: Built click-to-add modules, hover re-ordering (left/right swaps) and deletion controls, inline settings form to modify node labels, targets and delays, and custom toggle buttons for Human-in-the-loop enclaves.\n5. **Built Scrolling Trace Log Terminal**: Added a dynamic scrolling trace console displaying detailed telemetry logs mapping out in real time as the simulator runs.\n6. **Programmed Code Schema Exporters**: Provided real-time compiled JSON schemas and YAML manifests, complete with working 'Copy to Clipboard' and 'Download Spec File' triggers.\n7. **Added Cross-Tool Navigation**: Integrated custom navigator cards leading users to the GFF Zero-Trust Sandbox (`/build/sandbox`) and Proposal Studio (`/build/proposal`), backed by a highly stylized `<PremiumCTA />` banner.\n8. **Ensured Pure and Standard Compliance**: Eliminated render-time impurities like `Date.now()`, substituting pure React state counters to pass strict React Compiler ESlint checks. Passed both build compiling and lint runs cleanly.","verified":true}}}
